    <h1> FOREST CAMP (Flat Lands)</h1>
    <h3> Do you enjoy being surrounded by trees? Then you're in the right place!!</h3> <br>
    <p> Forest camping provides you with the opportunity to live amongst nature and whether you choose a designated camping site or prefer wild camping, there are loads of brilliant places to venture to.  This is for people of all ages, who enjoy the refreshing air, smell of wood, and singing of birds.</p>
    <h3> Here are some few places where you can expereince this: (Within Negros Island)</h3>
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Outdoor-Recreation/Bayles-Camping-Grounds-537824659884194/"> 
    Bayle's Camping Ground</a><br>
  <a href="https://thehappytrip.com/2018/05/forest-camp-resort-valencia-negros-oriental/"> 
    Forest Camp Resort</a><br>
  <a href="https://www.facebook.com/jomaxpeak/"> 
    Jomax Peak</a><br>
  </div>
