          <h1> REFRESHING WATER</h1>
    <h3> Are you looking for a place to be refreshed? Then you're in the right place!!</h3> <br>
    <p> Most of us recognise the calming effect of a walk by the river or along a beach.
    But while the health benefits of green space are now well known, thanks to the pioneering research of Roger Ulrich and the Kaplans among others, little analysis has been made of "blue space" – the impact of the sea, rivers, lakes, and even urban water features on our health and wellbeing.
    </p>
    <h3> Here are some few places where you can expereince this: (Within Negros Island)</h3>
    <a href="https://thehappytrip.com/2018/05/mabinay-spring-travel-guide/"> 
    Mabinay Spring</a><br>
  <a href="https://thehappytrip.com/2019/01/guintubdan-mountain-resort-la-carlota-city-travel-guide/"> 
